author: Ben Kesslen
title: At least 28 spring breakers from Texas test positive for COVID-19
description: As those who tested positive self-isolate, dozens of others are being monitored as the city investigates the cluster of cases.
content:
A woman runs up a hill in Austin, Texas on March 25, 2020.Eric Gay / AP
At least 28 spring breakers from the Austin, Texas-area tested positive for coronavirus following a spring break trip to Mexico, Austin public health officials said on Tuesday.
